{"tid":879113,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"問下價都比人串","createTime":"2018-10-27T16:16:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T03:25:43.000Z","uid":218908,"like":2,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5829674d77c1a1d9d4e94df5f61003ce7bad1023","tid":879113,"uid":218908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:16:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CnrCc1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCnrCc1a.png&h=79ee1340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁呢排唔得閒 諗住遲少少先出去買 驚冇貨<br />\n好聲好氣問佢幾句就咁 點搞呀"},{"pid":"b08d1c443d13ac8d18cd6410017b215a65ca64e1","tid":879113,"uid":59192,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:18:53.000Z","msg":"一日,有隻兔仔突然好想食面包,<br />\n<br />\n緊係佢就出左去面包店買老闆<br />\n<br />\n兔:&quot;老闆,有無100個面包?&quot;<br />\n老闆:&quot;沒有&quot;<br />\n<br />\n第二日兔仔又黎問<br />\n<br />\n兔:&quot;老闆,有無100個面包?&quot;<br />\n老闆都是話無<br />\n<br />\n第三日兔仔又係咁問,答案都係一樣:無<br />\n兔仔就咁樣問,問左個老闆成一個月<br />\n<br />\n個老闆俾佢既熱誠打動左,終於都整左100個面包<br />\n<br />\n第2日兔仔都好似平常咁黎<br />\n<br />\n然後又問:&quot;老闆,有無100個面包?&quot;<br />\n<br />\n老闆好有自信咁話:&quot;有啦!&quot;<br />\n<br />\n之後兔仔就話<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&quot;咁唔該俾2個我啦&quot;"},{"pid":"878985f391a6c102846b6561ae3b110c7bc0c484","tid":879113,"uid":33886,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:19:38.000Z","msg":"人地講得冇錯喎  係第1句態度差D姐 你解釋完 又emoji又正常番 我覺得冇咩野"},{"pid":"211936dfe6e454bc68bed8f8cc137e8c5dd12b14","tid":879113,"uid":125380,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:21:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得樓主冇錯 賣game佬態度差都唔係一朝一夕既事"},{"pid":"3383f1e5213187fffb631559e6a3e572901fb707","tid":879113,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:24:26.000Z","msg":"第二句就應該反制佢啦仲繼續俾佢串<br />\n我依家就係問 你知定唔知？"},{"pid":"12988c38564e382a907c96c454acf2f4ed52237a","tid":879113,"uid":48631,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"cit